Package hatalskan

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Exam
    An Exam represents a single exam made up of student responses, statistics, and a version.
    ExamAnalyzer
    Responsible for generating the answer keys, answers, and exams.
    ExamKey
    Represents a structure to store an exam's list of responses including the name and location of the file.
    ExamScorer
    Computes a set of exams and provides statistics
    ExamStatistics
    Analyzes a list of student exams associated with a given test.
    PDFConverter
    Converts PDF types
    PolyLearnFile
    Represents a PolyLearn file that can be read from and written to.
    Student
    Represents a student who has a first name, a last name, and a CalPoly Username
    StudentExam
    Represents a marked student exam owned by a student
